<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">&#8220;Our Lives Are Not Tragedies&#8221;: A Conversation on Disability Rights</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
