<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/universal-benefits-will-help-people-with-disabilities-escape-poverty/">Universal Benefits Will Help People With Disabilities Escape Poverty</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The means-tested benefits model has trapped people with disabilities in poverty without a clear path out.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/jack-delaney/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Jack Delaney</a></span>, </dd>
