<article class="row hentry post-264091 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-ableism tag-activism tag-ada tag-disability-justice tag-disability-rights tag-sexual-assault section-humanrights primary_topic-human-rights" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
