<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/climate-crisis-stokes-flames-in-california-putting-disabled-people-at-risk/">Climate Crisis Stokes Flames in California, Putting Disabled People at Risk</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">PG&#038;E, the utility responsible for some of California&#8217;s deadliest fires, is hurting people by shutting off power.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/sharon-zhang/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Sharon Zhang</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
